      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and there isn't a single blemish to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look and fall in love!",
