    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated V8 with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service to ensure peak internal health. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides crisp, lightning-fast gear changes, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and variable M differential lock maintain factory-spec chassis dynamics. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior leather shows no bolster wear or UV degradation. A truly turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning driver.",
